Final Release Tag
git tag -a v1.0.0 -m "feat!: initial release of Clinic Management System v1.0.0

Features:
- JWT authentication with refresh token rotation
- Patient self-registration, doctor accounts created by admin only
- Role-based access control: Admin, Doctor, Patient
- Doctor schedule management with slot boundary validation
- Appointment booking with 11 real-world edge case checks
- Status workflow: Pending->Confirmed->Completed with NoShow and Cancelled
- Prescription management with doctor ownership enforcement
- Admin dashboard with live stats and date-range reports
- Doctor deactivation with cascade appointment cancellation and token revocation
- EF Core with stored procedures — database-first, schema owned by SQL scripts
- NUnit unit tests: 59 tests across 5 service classes using Moq and FluentAssertions
- React 18 Vite frontend with role-based routing and JWT auto-refresh"

